  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK80">
<l>aṉpiṉ vaḻiya tuyirnilai yaḵtilārk</l>
<l>keṉputōl pōrtta vuṭampu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The seat of the soul is what lies on the path of love; for those who lack it,</l>
<l>the body merely covers bones with skin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
